	<name>Arduino IDE v2</name>
	<summary>Open-source electronics prototyping platform</summary>
	<developer_name>Arduino SA</developer_name>

	<description>
		<p>
            Arduino is an open-source electronics prototyping platform based
            on flexible, easy-to-use hardware and software.  It's intended for
            artists, designers, hobbyists, and anyone interested in creating
            interactive objects or environments.
        </p>
		<p>
            Included is an integrated development environment that can be used
            to develop and upload code to compatible microcontrollers.
        </p>
		<p>
            This is version 2 of the Arduino IDE. Version 2 is currently still in beta.
		</p>
		<p>
			The Flatpak build of Arduino IDE 2.x requires the user to have USB permissions to upload a sketch, preferably, the user has to be part of the dialout group.
		</p>
		<p>
			Alternatively, add the following 2 lines to /etc/udev/rules.d/50-arduino.rules:
		</p>
		<p>
			KERNEL=="ttyUSB[0-9]*",MODE="0666"
		</p>
		<p>
			KERNEL=="ttyACM[0-9]*",MODE="0666"
		</p>
	</description>

	<releases>
		<release version="2.0.0-rc7" date="2022-06-09">
			<description>
				<ul>
					<li>Updated to version 2 release candidate 7. github.com/arduino/arduino-ide/releases/tag/2.0.0-rc7</li>
					<li>Fix monitor service id creation. </li>
					<li>Added logging when restoring the layout data. </li>
					<li>Avoid opening duplicate editor tabs. </li>
					<li>Editor manager should be singleton. </li>
					<li>Pluggable monitor. </li>
					<li>Speed up IDE startup time. </li>
					<li>Updated translation files. </li>
					<li>Follow up 944: authentication sessions are not persistent. </li>
					<li>Use `clang-format` as the default sketch formatter. </li>
					<li>Dark theme implementation. </li>
					<li>Fixed LS stops working after OS sleep/wakeup cycle. </li>
					<li>Save dialog for closing temporary sketch and unsaved files. </li>
					<li>Fix duplicated editor tabs. </li>
					<li>Relaxed the Node version: `^14.x`. </li>
					<li>Updated Theia to 1.25.0. </li>
					<li>#944: Fixed auth. sessions not persistent. </li>
					<li>#985: Restored the missing `inject` decorator.  </li>
					<li>Allow flexibility in OS type selections in issue forms. </li>
					<li>Updated translation files. </li>
					<li>Save all open editors before running `Save As`. </li>
					<li>ignore workspace root check in changelog workflow. </li>
				</ul>
